name: Khalil Hazzard
bio: 1/2 of Self Scientific, 3X Grammy winning producer from Los Angeles. Credits: Dr Dre, Eminem, Jay Z, Kendrick, Drake, Pink, Nas, etc.

social_posts.post_text:
Game changer. Just a warning, now that Stems in Serato Studio 2.0 is officially out, you’re gonna hear the words “game changer” a lot.

DJ Khalil is saying it; “Stems is just a game changer”. Boston Chery’s saying it, “Just a game-changer really.” Dibia$e? You guessed it, he’s saying it too: "Stems is a game changer for me.”

To celebrate the release of Serato Studio 2.0, these three influential producers will, over the coming weeks, invite us into their musical worlds, walk us through their creative process, and show us how Stems in Serato Studio is revolutionising how they make music. 

Get your hands on this *technology and unlock your sound with Stems in Serato Studio 2.0
*Hint: It’s a game-changer.

#UPDATE Congratulations @djkhalil on another #grammy win with Best Rap Album for Kendrick Lamar’s Mr. Morale and the Big Steppers 🎉👏🎉👏

“People create, and then it affects the world forever … It’s the greatest feeling, because it’s powerful.” - @djkhalil 2023 Grammy nominee and multi-Grammy award winner.

Congratulations and good luck to all the artists and creators being recognised and honored at the 2023 Grammy Awards today 👏🥂🎉

DJ Khalil is up for two more Grammy awards - “Album of the Year” and “Best Rap Album” for his work on Kendrick Lamar’s Mr. Morale & The Big Steppers 👑

✨ As one of the stars of our “Serato Stems presents” campaign we can’t wait to share more from DJ Khalil over the coming weeks 💫👀

#grammy #grammys #grammys2023

What a night! I had the best father/ daughter date ever and we won for Best Rap Album with @kendricklamar 
Definitely a bucket list moment for me.

Thank you to everyone that helped make Naima’s night special. 

@jaleesahazzard @coachhazz42 @myssmoxie @stacyebranchemakeup @bellikemike 

And a big shout to @beverlyhillsluxrides for taking us in style. We had a blast!!

“I’m literally able to blend every genre now like never before.” - @djkhalil 

What began as a curiosity for making beats and a Casio sampler given to him by his mom, became a rich career of working with “bucket list” artists like Dr Dre, Eminem and Kendrick Lamar, who he has just won the Grammy for Best Rap album with 👑 At the centre of DJ Khalil’s music making ecosystem is Serato Studio. 🪐 Find out why Stems in Serato Studio 2.0 is opening up a whole new universe for him.

Plus, head to the link in bio to watch how DJ Khalil uses Stems in Serato Studio to make a beat using samples from Regional Garland and @karl.hector.malcouns from @nowagain records 🔪⚡️

#seratostudio #seratostems

DJ Khalil says Stems in Serato Studio has opened up a whole new world for him, and we want you to have that same experience! Enter our DJ Khalil Serato Studio 2.0 Remix Competition and get creative with #seratostems in #seratostudio. We’re giving you access to the same Regional Garland and Karl Hector samples DJ Khalil uses in his ‘Serato Stems presents’ video.

Join our Discord for the full Ts&Cs pinned at the top of our ‘💥stems-remix-competition’ channel + make sure you check out the ‘Serato Stems presents DJ Khalil’ video on YouTube for inspiration 🧠 (Both at the link in bio).

“The power of music is, I mean, for me personally, it is therapy. You know what I mean? It's therapy. I always say music can change the molecules in the room.” - @djkhalil 

Head to the link in bio to watch Khalil at work with Stems in Serato Studio 2.0.

#seratostudio #SeratoStems

Serato Studio 🤝 NBA on in the background. Who else needs a game on in the background while cookin’ up? | Swipe through to see all of @djkhalil’s favorite Tools of the Trade.

⚡️Basketball game on (mandatory)
⚡️Roland SP-404
⚡️Maestro Rhythm n Sound
⚡️KORG Minilogue
⚡️Jesse Dean Portable Turntable
⚡️Coke Zero
⚡️Black Corporation Deckard’s Dream

#UPDATE: Tune in 22 Feb | 12pm PST / 3pm EST / 8pm BST 
Twitch.tv/serato

In this special episode of Unscripted, multi-Grammy Award winner @djkhalil will sit down with @kutcorners for an in-depth chat about his career and love for music and production, and an insight into what it’s like working with his idols.

Plus, he’ll be listening to some of your submissions from our @seratostudio 2.0 Remix Competition live, and picking the top three beats. So make sure you get your beats into our Discord ASAP ⚡️⚡️⚡️(link to Discord in bio)

‘The Future of Sampling’ presented by @seratostudio and @beatclub with special guests @timbaland and @djkhalil 🎧🎶

⏰ March 7, 5pm EST 

You still have time to sign up at the link in bio 🎉 Registrations close March 7 at 4pm EST.
A true superhero. My best friend. Happy Bday Dad. We love you and we miss you.

Proud of you @coachhazz42 

First of many. Dad and Jalal are smiling right now. We are so proud of you. Nobody knows the work you put in to chase your dream, but we have seen it daily. Love you brother. Keep going!!
My best friend. We love you mom. Thank you for being an amazing example to all of us. Happy Mother’s Day @jaleesahazzard
We celebrate you today and everyday. Happy birthday Mom!!! We are so grateful for you. Enjoy your day mother, you deserve it. We love you @jaleesahazzard
Yesterday was a tough one. Happy Birthday big brother. Life is not the same without you. Our family is not the same without you but your spirit is here with us. We love you Jalal.

Great men, great fathers. We miss you everyday dad and Jalal.
Happy Father’s Day to all of the dads that show up for their families. You are appreciated.
8?????!!!!! Time is flying. Happy Bday Naima Joy. I keep saying this but you really are a dream come true. You are everything and more. I am so proud of you. Happy Bday my Naima, I love you.

Happy Bday @coachhazz42 aka Uncle Toots!!
Your commitment to the game and to your family is always inspiring. We love you!! The best is yet to come!!

Grateful to work with some of the most amazing artists in the world. @jonbatiste you are special human being and one of the most creative artists on this planet. Shout out to the one woman choir @nikkigrier and @chiefseeff for adding life to this song on bass. It’s always a pleasure producing with the super talented @rogetchahayed and @wesleysingerman
Can’t forget brother @thankugoodsir for your brilliant “words”
World Music Radio Out now!

#GUnit - “Lay You Down” prod. by #DJKhalil samples “Doctor Marvell” by #Klaatu #SampleBible 

@djkhalil

One of best creative experiences of my life. Big shout out to @_imdrewski for introducing me to one of the most talented young artists I’ve ever worked with. Congrats to my brother @nasty_csa for delivering an amazing body of work. You have arrived brother!
Shout out to all of the producers, artists, writers, engineers and musicians that contributed to this album. Working in SA was a dream come true. 

Thank you @nikkigrier @in2mixin @chiefseeff @sambarsh @dontaewinslow @chace_infinite @jaycenjoshua for always delivering.
@maxonproduction_  and our brother Mike for your hard work.

Thank you @tunji for your support. This is a full circle moment.

Nasty C “I Love it Here” out now!!!

Executive Produced by @_princekb_  @colinfgayle and myself
AOTY!! Grateful!!! Shout out to my brother @jonbatiste on his nominations. This makes 4 AOTY noms in 3 years. Unreal. Congrats to everyone involved!!
6!!!!!!!! Happy Bday Amari!! I am so proud of you. You are a kind, smart, loving, funny and determined young man. Keep getting buckets son! The world is yours! We love you!!!
